            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1639400860881-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1639400860881-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>free range chicken breast portion[s]</strong> into rough bite-sized pieces</p><p>Return the reserved pan to a high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong>, and once hot add the <strong>chopped chicken</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until browned</p><p>Once browned, add your <strong>ground turmeric</strong> and cook for a further 1 min</p><p>Transfer the<strong> browned chicken</strong> to a plate, reserve the pan and <strong>juices</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1639400868422-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
