          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-7-1639400899844-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Keralan-style free range chicken curry</strong> with the <strong>lime & chilli rice</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped chilli</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and a<strong> lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
